profile_positions.description:
Key projects: 
- delivery of the Retailer and Advertiser API to external partners;
- work on enablers for the area's strategy.

Key outcomes:
- contribution to cross-alignment between the teams in the area;
- delivery of key features (VAT invoices, Share of Voice reports) in the new API version which are increasing partners' NPS.

Key responsibilities:
- stakeholder management;
- backlog management;
- writing functional requirements;
- API acceptance testing;
- elaboration of the roadmap;
- prioritisation.
